cs.SY, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.NE 

The paper deals with the problem of certifying stability of reinforcement learning policies when interconnected with nonlinear dynamical systems. This problem lies at the intersection of control theory and reinforcement learning. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.SY (Systems and Control), followed by cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.RO (Robotics), and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
